Standard Bank Group Ltd. said its
loan book for affordable homes has climbed to 10 billion rand
and that it expects to double that figure by 2015, Nicholas
Nkosi, director for affordable housing, said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
